CrawlItem.Text: Great Chinese for Zagreb - just ordered from them again and hope their beef and broccoli will be as good as their Chinese noodles with shrimps was! Glad to have a new place to order from in the neighborhood :)

SentenceInfo.Text: grleta finese fora zagreb - gust odereš farom trem gani nad hipe hir blef nad broccoli ili beg as good as hir finese noodles tih shrimps as !
glad to halve a ne place to orden farom ni tihe neighborhood : )
